// Portfolio Modal 4
#portfolioModal4.portfolio-modal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', aria-labelledby='portfolioModal4', aria-hidden='true')
    .modal-dialog.modal-xl
        .modal-content
            .modal-header.border-0
                button.btn-close(type='button', data-bs-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
            .modal-body.text-center.pb-5
                .container
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-8
                            // Portfolio Modal - Title
                            h2.portfolio-modal-title.text-secondary.text-lowercase.mb-0 Carousel with captions
                            // Icon Divider
                            .divider-custom
                                .divider-custom-line
                            // Portfolio Modal - Carousel with captions
                            #carouselCaptions.carousel.slide(data-bs-ride='carousel')
                                .carousel-indicators
                                    button.btn-light.active(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='0', aria-label='Slide 1', aria-current='true')
                                    button.btn-light(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='1', aria-label='Slide 2')
                                    button.btn-light(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='2', aria-label='Slide 3')
                                .carousel-inner.rounded.mb-5
                                    .carousel-item.active
                                        img.d-block.w-100(src='assets/img/portfolio/carousel-captions-1.jpg', alt='...')
                                        .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
                                            h5.text-white.text-lowercase Cheeseburgers are like a metaphor for life
                                    .carousel-item
                                        img.d-block.w-100(src='assets/img/portfolio/carousel-captions-2.jpg', alt='...')
                                        .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
                                            h5.text-white.text-lowercase All the good stuff is in the middle
                                    .carousel-item
                                        img.d-block.w-100(src='assets/img/portfolio/carousel-captions-3.jpg', alt='...')
                                        .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
                                            h5.text-white.text-lowercase But the rest of it is necessary too
                                button.carousel-control-prev(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselCaptions', data-bs-slide='prev')
                                    span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
                                    span.visually-hidden
                                        | Previous
                                button.carousel-control-next(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselCaptions', data-bs-slide='next')
                                    span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
                                    span.visually-hidden 
                                        | Next
                            // Portfolio Modal - Text
                            .text-black.text-start.mb-4
                                p Think of cheeseburgers like a Tinder match. They might not all be your soulmate but you've gotta find out to be sure. It can get a little messy and that's just part of the fun.
                                p Some are cheesy, others can be a little dry, and the rare few are a disaster. There are so many cheeseburgers out there it can be hard to commit to just one favourite. That being said, when you know, you just know.
                                p Everyone has their perfect match. Sometimes it's just around the corner, other times you have to travel the world in search of it. Wherever your perfect cheeseburger is, it's out there.
                            button.btn.btn-primary(data-bs-dismiss='modal')
                                | Close